title: God Is A Rewarder | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: God Is A Rewarder | Joel Osteen
description:
God promises to reward those who diligently seek Him. When you make Him a priority, He will fill you with His strength, wisdom and favor. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
